#3. JSP 
	
		1. HTML 
		2. CSS
		3. JS + JQUERY
		4. JSP 			+ SERBLET	 + ORACLE 
		(VIEW:JAVA+HTML) (CONTROLLER) (MODEL)
		
		실습 : 
		 html : hyper text markup language
		 <>   : 브라우저야 ~해석해
		 <html> : 엘리먼트 -해석내용
		 head : 문서정보
		 body : 문서내용
		 
		 ==>> html5
		 <!doctype>
		 <html>
		 	<head></head>
		 	<body></body>
		 </html>
		 
